Kanyike with 16,053 votes. 
  Rubabo in Rukungiri will be represented by Mr. Henry 
Tumukunde with 16,630 votes. Bwamba County is to be represented 
by Dr. Constantine Kamanda Bataringaya, who garnered 13,901 
votes. Tororo District, Samia Bugwe County North electoral area 
