Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Qian Qichen, Chinese vice premier and foreign 
minister who is currently visiting Bangladesh, called on 
President Abdur Rahman Biswas at the President's House yesterday 
morning. The two sides held talks in a cordial atmosphere. 
During the talks, Foreign Minister Qian Qichen conveyed the 
