<H3> <TI>   Jiang Zemin Cables 'Arafat </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2702124594 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0956 
GMT 27 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2702124594 </F>
