Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, 27 Feb (XINHUA) -- President Jiang Zemin 
sent a cable message to Palestinian President Yasir 'Arafat on 
26 February to express his strong condemnation of the serious 
atrocity of killing innocent Palestinian civilians on West Bank 
on 25 February and expressed his deep sympathy to the families 
